{{zh-forms|alt=𦶛,𦱤,䒬}}
From {{och-l|無|there is no}} + distributive suffix *''-k'' ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). For the same type of derivation, see the relationship of {{och-l|有|there is}} and {{och-l|或|some}}.
